metadata.name: Transnaturalism 1
metadata.description:
This artwork is the result of my work, which has nature as its main theme, and artificial intelligence, which has reinterpreted these plants, giving them new meanings and colors.
I wanted to deepen the concept that our society currently puts us in dichotomy with our fellow men, or you are with or you are against, vax - novax, black and white, good and bad, creating contrasts that seem unsolvable. But underground these plants, which seem distant, talk to each other, intertwine their roots in the common soil.
